# Clean Minimalist Aesthetic Update: Bento Boxes Focus

Following your guidance, we are pivoting the primary focus of this aesthetic cleanup specifically to the animations inside the Bento Boxes (`LandingFeatures.tsx`). Currently, these dynamic previews heavily utilize rainbow colors (blue, green, amber, primary) to denote states, buttons, and charts. 

We will strip away these colored accents in favor of a striking, high-contrast monochrome (Black & White) aesthetic that feels more premium.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This plan aggressively replaces almost all colors within the Bento Box animations with `foreground` (black in light mode/white in dark mode), `background`, and `neutral` shades. Please review the detailed component breakdowns below to ensure this strict B&W aesthetic matches your vision.

## Proposed Changes

---

### [LandingFeatures.tsx](file:///C:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/prod-adecos/src/containers/landing/LandingFeatures.tsx)

We will update all four animated previews in the Bento Grid to use strict monochrome styling. 

#### 1. AIAgentPreview (Chat Animation)
- **Chat Bubbles:** Invert the user message bubble from `bg-primary text-white` to `bg-foreground text-background`. 
- **Status & Typing Indicators:** Change the online green dot to `bg-foreground`, and the typing dots from `bg-primary/60` to `bg-foreground/50`.
- **Chart Animation:** Replace the blue and green CTR/CVR bars with `bg-foreground` and `bg-foreground/40`.
- **Action Plan Widget:** Remove the blue background/borders (`bg-blue-500/5`), changing it to a sharp neutral theme (e.g., `bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-900 border-l-foreground`). Change the green "High Impact" badge to `bg-foreground text-background`. Replace the blue "Apply Strategy" button with a sleek `bg-foreground text-background`.

#### 2. DeepResearchPreview (Scanning Animation)
- **Progress Bars:** Change the scanning laser and progress bars from `bg-primary` to `bg-foreground`.
- **Search Cursor:** Make the blinking search cursor `bg-foreground`.
- **Results & Status:** Remove the green text from "20% Định kỳ", relying instead on font-weight and layout. Change the green "Verified" checkmark chip to `bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-foreground`.

#### 3. AnalyticsPreview (Charts & KPIs)
- **KPI Metrics:** The values for Copy Profit, Notion Comm, and Avg CPA currently use green, blue, and amber text. We will standardize all KPI numbers to a bold `text-foreground`.
- **Badges:** Change the green `+40% ROI` badge to a premium `bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-foreground border-border`.
- **Area Chart:** Update the SVG stroke and gradient stops from `var(--primary)` to use `var(--foreground)` and context-aware transparency.

#### 4. ProjectManagementPreview (Dashboard Modals)
- **State Changes:** The "Connect Ads" and "Ref Count" boxes currently turn blue and green when activated. We will change the active state to a high-contrast inverted look: `bg-foreground text-background` to clearly denote activation without relying on color.
- **Labels & Tags:** Update the top-left "Project" tag from `bg-primary/10 text-primary` to `bg-foreground text-background`.
- **Modal Buttons:** The "Saving..." modal buttons, currently `bg-primary`, will become `bg-foreground text-background`.

